metadata.name: Wagmi Apes Unrevealed
metadata.description: The WAGMI APES started in 2023, as a result of experiments from different NFT Creators. As time passed, the Apes began to recognize the harm humans were causing them. In an epic movement, Chief Ape led the Apes to freedom. United, The WAGMI APES grew and thrived and continues to operate around the world.
